Education

The educational landscape of Midland County is primarily served by two major school districts:

*   [Midland Independent School District](/Midland_Independent_School_District)
*   [Greenwood Independent School District](/Greenwood_Independent_School_District)

While most of the county falls within the service area of [Midland College](/Midland_College), the community of Greenwood is situated outside this particular district's purview, indicating a degree of localized educational service provision.

